{"type": "article", "id": 6751, "title": "Beolit 15 无线音箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-25T07:19:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234224tgjI7X9qeGDJWRZh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦高端视听品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen 日前邀请丹麦女设计师 Cecilie Manz 为其 Beolit 系列再添一款新品 Beolit 15，延续了 Beolit 12 提手篮式的外形特征，采用样机氧化铝制作机身外壳，搭配粒面皮革手带，顶部还设有防滑橡胶托盘。整个机身重量达 2.7 kg，采用二分频设计，峰值功率可达 240 瓦。此外，Beolit 15 还兼有 蓝牙 4.0 与 True360 全方位音频技术，电池续航时间达 24 小时。提供香槟金、极地蓝与浅玫红色 3 种选择。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234221RbJNB4Vxe1Uvf2kA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71515892\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234221jklLEApHdb5ZQoyI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72493888\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234222BXp4r3iUbxzTVI6F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72616137\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234222LYyJHIuKF9pC60bm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67359413\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234223MfNg1uP7bIkJdSVZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72249389\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342239tyXclekL6WUHT7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70904645\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}